<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Your Pre-saved Song is Out Now!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .email-container {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .header .emoji {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .announcement {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .song-info {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .song-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .artist-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .platform-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .listen-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .listen-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6);
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            margin: 20px 0;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .highlight {
            background: #fff3cd;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .footer-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer-brand {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .social-icons {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #ddd, transparent);
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="emoji">ðŸŽ‰</div>
            <h1>It's Out Now!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hello {{name}},</p>
            
            <p class="message">
                The moment you've been waiting for is here! The song you pre-saved is now <span class="highlight">live and ready to stream</span>.
            </p>
            
            <div class="announcement">
                <div class="song-info">
                    <p class="song-title">"{{songTitle}}"</p>
                    <p class="artist-name">by {{artistName}}</p>
                    <div class="platform-badge">{{platform}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="message">
                Click the button below to start listening right now on <strong>{{platform}}</strong>!
            </p>
            
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{platformUrl}}" class="listen-button">ðŸŽµ Listen Now on {{platform}}</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p class="message" style="font-size: 14px; color: #888;">
                Thank you for pre-saving and supporting this release. Your early support helps artists reach more fans and grow their music careers!
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                Thank you for supporting independent music!
            </p>
            <p class="footer-brand">
                ðŸŽµ The RatedaFRiKa Team
            </p>
            <p class="footer-text" style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 20px;">
                You received this email because you signed up for a presave on RatedaFRiKa.<br>
                We hope you enjoy the music!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

